{"word":"Uzziel","slug":"uzziel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Uzziel</b> <a href=\"#/H5816\">H5816</a> <br/> 1. A son of Kohath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=18'>Exo 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=22'>Exo 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=4'>Lev 10:4</a><br/> 2. A Simeonite captain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=42'>1Ch 4:42</a><br/> 3. Son of Bela<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=7'>1Ch 7:7</a><br/> 4. One of David's musicians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=4'>1Ch 25:4</a><br/> 5. A Levite, son of Jeduthun<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=14'>2Ch 29:14</a><br/> 6. A goldsmith, aided in repairing the walls of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=8'>Neh 3:8</a>"}]}